Understanding the BOM-Link URN

The key line is:
{
  "url": "urn:cdx:aaaaaaaa-bbbb-cccc-dddd-eeeeeeeeeeee/2"
}


This means:

Part                                    Meaning
====                                    =======
urn:cdx:                                CycloneDX BOM-Link namespace
aaaaaaaa-bbbb-cccc-dddd-eeeeeeeeeeee    Target BOM serial number UUID
/2                                      BOM version

The referenced BOM must therefore contain:
{
  "serialNumber": "urn:uuid:aaaaaaaa-bbbb-cccc-dddd-eeeeeeeeeeee",
  "version": 2
}

This creates a deterministic immutable link.

Recommended Repository Layout

    sboms/
    ├── applications/
    │   └── advisor-chatbot/
    │       └── 1.9.0/
    │           └── advisor-chatbot-1.9.0.sbom.json
    │
    └── aiboms/
        └── advisor-llm/
            └── 8.1/
                └── advisor-llm-8.1.aibom.json